 subject="Tails, Tor and BitTorrent"
 date="2011-06-27T07:10:44Z"
 content="""
Tails does not ship any BitTorrent software and is unlikely to do so
in the future: using BitTorrent over Tor is generally considered to
harm the Tor network.

See, [Tor Project: Bittorrent over Tor isn't a good idea](https://blog.torproject.org/blog/bittorrent-over-tor-isnt-good-idea).

